{"tid":1685004,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"本港財年首6個月赤字954億元","createTime":"2019-10-31T10:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T16:01:36.000Z","uid":284699,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e0ff6e05231bcf52aa08bb490a91f2250ff165","tid":1685004,"uid":284699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:57:01.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】政府公布本財政年度首6個月財務狀況，整體開支2817億元，收入1800億元。計入在政府綠色債券計劃下發行的綠色債券所得淨收入78億元及償還為數15億元的機構票據後，本財政年度首6個月的財務狀況為954億元赤字。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，截至9月份的赤字主要是由於薪俸稅及利得稅等主要收入均大多在財政年度的後期收取。 財政儲備在9月30日為10755億港元。"},{"pid":"8283dbb905b23ec6597140df7643e6bc7f22a755","tid":1685004,"uid":51814,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:00:44.000Z","msg":"又cap水做維穩費"},{"pid":"6edf623ca54579c74269c3008d14c2bd585b606a","tid":1685004,"uid":32352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:04:05.000Z","msg":"Ot錢都洗唔少啦"},{"pid":"708844e034aaf9c7a824d6326fba911f89d32c48","tid":1685004,"uid":210190,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:19:28.000Z","msg":"每年頭三季都係咁架 冇咩特別"},{"pid":"c0b042c7091a262d487a2f01ae27e291ac60651e","tid":1685004,"uid":50214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"稅季記住用pps<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e015118425c0cc0abf996a627cc44676040297d","tid":1685004,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:49:52.000Z","msg":"舊年同期？"},{"pid":"697b43977b1cf39d00d1874177fae20ab93e498e","tid":1685004,"uid":3302,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T12:53:43.000Z","msg":"攬炒成績表：B+<br />\n班主任評語：天資聰穎 具謀略 捨己為群 惜處事略欠穩重 做事衝動 宜三思而後行 仍有進步空間"},{"pid":"6229dae64ad85e935fbc06800adc700bf937e797","tid":1685004,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:05:55.000Z","msg":"首6咋 未示威架"},{"pid":"a846c1ba0cfe2606860862599c4195d3bdaed384","tid":1685004,"uid":5067,"lik